name: Close Encounters series 2 #005: Roswell Incident
description:
Based upon the events that took place on Rowsell, New Mexico in 1947; where a space ship crashed with four extraterrestrial beings inside. Three of them died in the accident, while the fourth one (later named "EBE") was held captive and interrogated for several years, until it's death.
